{"tid":1255661,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［睇到火滾］抗爭都要用腦嫁","createTime":"2019-06-24T14:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T16:01:04.000Z","uid":115613,"like":9,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ccacaa61d715c6f9e807ac55f4f65e0ca69bf15e","tid":1255661,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T14:56:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FNW7Qxm5SiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFNW7Qxm5SiU&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=f1d009dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FNW7Qxm5SiU</a><br />\n<br />\n喂大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有時示威既手法都要用腦諗下有乜效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同有乜影響<br />\n你班豬隊友今次咁撚on9 玩Lift 又沒得著<br />\n仲有班官講野同手法都大方得體過你地好多<br />\n林鄭同啲高官只會笑鳩你地小學雞打爛仔架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />炸<br />\n<br />\n如果沒人lead住抗爭<br />\n我寧願你地做鍵盤戰士<br />\n<br />\n成場抗爭唔想比你班爛仔搞到鑊哂"},{"pid":"92cc745b8f4476f6240a27760504451ae937bb47","tid":1255661,"uid":7716,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T15:13:31.000Z","msg":"你唔出黎lead住啲人?<br />\n群眾自發就係咁架啦<br />\n一係你就出黎帶領<br />\n人地做完又係到屌 屌撚左成日仲未夠?<br />\n到人地個個唔出黎得返鍵盤戰士你就真係最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4de678c3dd38e9619d963ae66e57cd9cbe628a","tid":1255661,"uid":126783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T15:17:09.000Z","msg":"大家唔好理佢"},{"pid":"469463d97050741c02e4a5676a451bffd4ab0c4c","tid":1255661,"uid":115613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"92cc745b8f4476f6240a27760504451ae937bb4